{"tid":1158783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱食食下M記，突然有隻蝗幼蟲飛咗喺我隔離","createTime":"2019-05-17T08:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T23:38:48.000Z","uid":167330,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"57d3199a2088ea69842dc6af957bb2ecc2b7fd31","tid":1158783,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"以為佢坐低等位，點知佢一坐低就瘋狂揼枱面，揼撚到嘭嘭聲，而且張枱仲震到仆街，嚴重打擾我食野，佢揼咗5秒左右，我忍咗佢，之後佢就十行開咗。<br />\n<br />\n點知過咗5秒，佢飛返返嚟繼續揼鳩張枱，於是我就話咗佢一句：「咪揼得唔得？」點知佢唔理我，繼續瘋狂㪣奏佢嘅交響樂，我忍唔住，以中等聲量閙佢：「咪再敲得唔得？你阻住其他人食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」 點知隻幼蟲竟然喺到陰笑，繼續敲枱，敲敲下又飛走咗。<br />\n<br />\n點知又過咗5秒，佢又飛返返嚟，繼續敲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今次我忍唔住，勁大聲鬧：「你再阻住其他人食野，我就去叫經理出嚟！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZpYaLb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZpYaLb.gif&h=6bfa5f66&s={SIZE}\" />  」 今次大聲到半間M記都聽到，附近嘅人都望過嚟。而最令人扯火嘅係，佢老母望咗一眼之後竟然若無其事咁繼續等餐，而隻幼蟲繼續陰笑住，停咗2秒，之後細細力咁繼續敲，有一刻我想一巴車落佢到，奈何如果我咁做，輸蝕嘅係我<br />\n<br />\n好在又過咗幾秒，兩隻蝗終於一齊飛走咗"},{"pid":"2ddfecf3fd58ce779723ad67d5ed0610225b5092","tid":1158783,"uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"敲佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c6fa4a4e3277dc53e159fd049b3fba775ef10c","tid":1158783,"uid":167330,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一入到去用點餐機已經有隻蝗幼蟲走埋嚟拍打部點餐機，阻住我點餐，佢家長企喺隔離望住，竟然乜都唔做。<br />\n<br />\n而且有堆幼蟲喺度爬個counter，但都冇人制止，嗰刻真係好在個counter同啲飲管機跌落嚟壓撚死佢，屌你老母呢間M記我會永久blacklist<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyRWGU4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgyRWGU4.gif&h=2cfc2f46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb71175199b9f0a7e308aeb005d654d2e5b39ba7","tid":1158783,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ddfecf3fd58ce779723ad67d5ed0610225b5092","tid":1158783,"uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"敲佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"我應該會俾人拉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kr8RvOL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkr8RvOL.gif&h=9398822f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e26d7ea39bbd6b5f96750cfdf250b3c5f8e41286","tid":1158783,"uid":1425,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"鬧人用問句黎, 鬧都鬧得冇啲霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87afc944696dc5a321bbebc8eea711fef21f95f","tid":1158783,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fb71175199b9f0a7e308aeb005d654d2e5b39ba7","tid":1158783,"uid":167330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ddfecf3fd58ce779723ad67d5ed0610225b5092","tid":1158783,"uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"敲佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"我應該會俾人拉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kr8RvOL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkr8RvOL.gif&h=9398822f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"香港殺昆蟲暫時唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b6b3c7c30e94ead8d3661ecb525245ea2bbb91","tid":1158783,"uid":44646,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"直接同佢老母開拖：<br />\n<br />\n你老母有無教你要有禮貌呀？"},{"pid":"79c909abf98da69fa3d7e00ab5cdc6e531834472","tid":1158783,"uid":280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"我會一巴車埋去.....屌你阻尻住我食野..."},{"pid":"2fa4f784fb631008f551f0926677a46517008c32","tid":1158783,"uid":82542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20